data.description: Hey house hunters, forget FOMO! You DON'T want to miss this one. This cutie is the triple threat—3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and so much pizzazz your grandma’s pearls will feel dull. Walk in and let the vaulted ceilings sweep you off your feet!  Cool as a cucumber? Nah, be cooler than a whole salad with the BRAND NEW AC unit for when the weather turns stifling again. Ah, the great room. It's not just great; it’s Tony-the-Tiger GRRREAT! Perfect for movie nights, interpretive dances, or a solo karaoke session!  Green thumb alert! Turn the abundant garden space into your own Eden or grow zucchinis the size of submarines. The world is your oyster—or your vegetable patch. And hey, there's even a shed for when you need to hide from your responsibilities. Close to all the amenities and highway!
